<concept xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="specifying-document-opening-preferences" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:concept.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Specifying Document Opening Preferences</title>
  <conbody id="body">
    <p>Document opening preferences include the following:<ol>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="specifying-file-types.xml">File extensions</xref> that will be offered in the <keyword>Open Document Dialog</keyword> and the <keyword>Open Document with Template Dialog</keyword> when you browse for a file to open.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="specifying-xml-files-search-path.xml">The value of the variable <codeph>
                <varname>$SERNA_XML.</varname>
              </codeph></xref></p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="specifying-xml-catalogs.xml">Paths to XML Catalogs.</xref></p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="specifying-dtds.xml">Paths to DTDs.</xref></p>
        </li>
      </ol></p>
  </conbody>
</concept>
